#. <section class="sutta" id="an3.124"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.124:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.124:0.2"
msgid "13. Kusināravagga"
msgstr "13. Kusināra"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.124:0.3"
msgid "124. Bhaṇḍanasutta"
msgstr "124. Arguments"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an3.124:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Yassaṃ, bhikkhave, disāyaṃ bhikkhū bhaṇḍanajātā kalahajātā vivādāpannā "
"aññamaññaṃ mukhasattīhi vitudantā viharanti, manasi kātumpi me esā, "
"bhikkhave, disā na phāsu hoti, pageva gantuṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I’m not even comfortable thinking about a place where "
"mendicants argue—quarreling and fighting, continually wounding each other "
"with barbed words—let alone going there."

msgctxt "an3.124:1.2"
msgid "Niṭṭhamettha gacchāmi:"
msgstr "I come to a conclusion about them:"

#. VAR: bahulamakaṃsu → bahulīmakaṃsu (s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an3.124:1.3"
msgid "‘addhā te āyasmanto tayo dhamme pajahiṃsu, tayo dhamme bahulamakaṃsu."
msgstr ""
"‘Clearly those venerables have given up three things and cultivated three "
"things.’"

msgctxt "an3.124:1.4"
msgid "Katame tayo dhamme pajahiṃsu?"
msgstr "What three things have they given up?"

msgctxt "an3.124:1.5"
msgid "Nekkhammavitakkaṃ, abyāpādavitakkaṃ, avihiṃsāvitakkaṃ—"
msgstr "Thoughts of renunciation, love, and kindness."

msgctxt "an3.124:1.6"
msgid "ime tayo dhamme pajahiṃsu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.124:1.7"
msgid "Katame tayo dhamme bahulamakaṃsu?"
msgstr "What three things have they cultivated?"

msgctxt "an3.124:1.8"
msgid "Kāmavitakkaṃ, byāpādavitakkaṃ, vihiṃsāvitakkaṃ—"
msgstr "Sensual, malicious, and cruel thoughts. …"

msgctxt "an3.124:1.9"
msgid "ime tayo dhamme bahulamakaṃsu’."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.124:1.10"
msgid ""
"Yassaṃ, bhikkhave, disāyaṃ bhikkhū bhaṇḍanajātā kalahajātā vivādāpannā "
"aññamaññaṃ mukhasattīhi vitudantā viharanti, manasi kātumpi me esā, "
"bhikkhave, disā na phāsu hoti, pageva gantuṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.124:1.11"
msgid "Niṭṭhamettha gacchāmi:"
msgstr "I come to a conclusion about them:"

msgctxt "an3.124:1.12"
msgid ""
"‘addhā te āyasmanto ime tayo dhamme pajahiṃsu, ime tayo dhamme "
"bahulamakaṃsu’."
msgstr ""
"‘Clearly those venerables have given up three things and built up three "
"things.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.276"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an3.124:2.1"
msgid ""
"Yassaṃ pana, bhikkhave, disāyaṃ bhikkhū samaggā sammodamānā avivadamānā "
"khīrodakībhūtā aññamaññaṃ piyacakkhūhi sampassantā viharanti, gantumpi me "
"esā, bhikkhave, disā phāsu hoti, pageva manasi kātuṃ."
msgstr ""
"I feel comfortable going to a place where the mendicants live in harmony—"
"appreciating each other, without quarreling, blending like milk and water, "
"and regarding each other with kindly eyes—let alone thinking about it."

msgctxt "an3.124:2.2"
msgid "Niṭṭhamettha gacchāmi:"
msgstr "I come to a conclusion about them:"

msgctxt "an3.124:2.3"
msgid "‘addhā te āyasmanto tayo dhamme pajahiṃsu, tayo dhamme bahulamakaṃsu."
msgstr ""
"‘Clearly those venerables have given up three things and built up three "
"things.’"

msgctxt "an3.124:2.4"
msgid "Katame tayo dhamme pajahiṃsu?"
msgstr "What three things have they given up?"

msgctxt "an3.124:2.5"
msgid "Kāmavitakkaṃ, byāpādavitakkaṃ, vihiṃsāvitakkaṃ—"
msgstr "Sensual, malicious, and cruel thoughts."

msgctxt "an3.124:2.6"
msgid "ime tayo dhamme pajahiṃsu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.124:2.7"
msgid "Katame tayo dhamme bahulamakaṃsu?"
msgstr "What three things have they built up?"

msgctxt "an3.124:2.8"
msgid "Nekkhammavitakkaṃ, abyāpādavitakkaṃ, avihiṃsāvitakkaṃ—"
msgstr "Thoughts of renunciation, love, and kindness. …"

msgctxt "an3.124:2.9"
msgid "ime tayo dhamme bahulamakaṃsu’."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.124:2.10"
msgid ""
"Yassaṃ, bhikkhave, disāyaṃ bhikkhū samaggā sammodamānā avivadamānā "
"khīrodakībhūtā aññamaññaṃ piyacakkhūhi sampassantā viharanti, gantumpi me "
"esā, bhikkhave, disā phāsu hoti, pageva manasi kātuṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.124:2.11"
msgid "Niṭṭhamettha gacchāmi:"
msgstr "I come to a conclusion about them:"

msgctxt "an3.124:2.12"
msgid ""
"‘addhā te āyasmanto ime tayo dhamme pajahiṃsu, ime tayo dhamme "
"bahulamakaṃsū’”ti."
msgstr ""
"‘Clearly those venerables have given up three things and built up three "
"things.’”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.124:2.13"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
